  - title: "Set the empty markers"
    description: |
      To set properties of the empty markers (the remainder of the grid), define a <em>last</em> `series` entry without a `value`. Note that creating an empty series will also cause a legend item to be created for it.
    config:
      data:
        - universal credit: 4
      total: 100
      columns:
        - name: "uc tooltip"
          template: "Claiming Universal Credit or Jobseeker's Allowance: {{ universal credit | toLocaleString() }}%"
      series:
        - value: "universal credit"
          title: "Claiming"
          colour: "#ce0058"
          tooltip: "uc tooltip"
          points:
            marker:
              svg: '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-person-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 14s-1 0-1-1 1-4 6-4 6 3 6 4-1 1-1 1H3Zm5-6a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6Z"/></svg>'
